----
update child
 ├── project
 │    ├── scan child
 │    │    └── flags: avoid-full-scan
 │    └── projections
 │         └── 4
 └── f-k-checks
      └── f-k-checks-item: child(p) -> parent(p)
           └── anti-join (lookup parent)
                ├── lookup columns are key
                ├── locking: for-share,durability-guaranteed
                ├── with-scan &1
                └── filters (true)

